# Researcher — bowling-shirt-designer

Build-prep package for demo-builder. Plan is locked (CEO: pass). All domain
research was resolved in pre-researcher.out and absorbed into the plan. This file
is implementation scaffolding only.

---

## 1. Library versions (pinned for React 18 compatibility)

```json
{
  "dependencies": {
    "next": "15.5.20",
    "react": "^18.3.1",
    "react-dom": "^18.3.1",
    "three": "^0.185.1",
    "@react-three/fiber": "8.18.0",
    "@react-three/drei": "9.122.0",
    "zustand": "^5.0.14",
    "tailwindcss": "^3.4.19",
    "autoprefixer": "^10.4.20",
    "postcss": "^8.5.6"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "@types/node": "^22",
    "@types/react": "^18",
    "@types/react-dom": "^18",
    "@types/three": "^0.168",
    "typescript": "^5.7.2"
  }
}
```

**Compatibility chain confirmed:** r3f 8.x requires React ^18 < 19; drei 9.x
requires @react-three/fiber ^8 + React ^18; Next.js 15.x supports React ^18.2.
Do NOT upgrade r3f to 9.x (requires React 19).

